════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Dataset: ../MBTI_500.csv
Seed: 42

Phase C v2 Quick Wins:
  🛡️  PURITY GATE (NEW):
     - Threshold: 0.025
     - Blocks: ESFJ (purity=0.009), ISFJ (0.016)
     - Prevents degradation from contaminated classes

  📊 Quality Gate Lowered:
     - 0.30 → 0.25 (allow more classes)

  💰 F1 Budget Thresholds Adjusted:
     - 0.35 0.20 → 0.40 0.20
     - Moves ESFP from HIGH (30×) to MID (70×) tier

  🌡️  Adaptive Temperature (from Phase C v1):
     - MID F1 (0.20-0.45): temp=0.5

Expected Improvement (vs Phase C v1: +0.06%):
  • MID-tier: +0.15% to +0.30%
  • Overall: +1.00% to +1.15%

